{"tid":263857,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老師 : 抱著跟老師啪啪啪的覺悟去比賽","createTime":"2017-05-30T11:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T12:07:28.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a452386d7100cfb5b158d4f61f1a96b6ee30257","tid":263857,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T11:00:04.000Z","msg":"日本堺市教育委員會29日指出，某所市立學校的56歲男師，擔任運動社團的顧問，以指導為由要女學生全裸，教育委員會予以免職處分。據《每日新聞》報導，教育委員會指出，該名男師在5月6日的比賽中，對輸掉的女學生訓話「抱著跟老師啪啪啪的覺悟去比賽」、「回去學校就來啪啪啪吧」，隔日，還在上課中將女學生叫出教室，到隔壁無人教室要求她全裸，訓完話後抱著穿上衣服的女學生「等成人以後就來啪啪啪吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女學生家屬知道後通報教育委員會，該名男師解釋「我沒有看到她的裸體，這只是希望她抱持必勝的覺悟去比賽」。是教育委員會詢問同社團約20名學生後，其中13人表示，男師曾對她們說「抱著跟老師親吻跟啪啪啪的覺悟吧」等性騷擾發言。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/recommend/20170530/1129229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Frecommend%2F20170530%2F1129229&d=iZQv5qoaQU151S%2Fpo1xTiYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=bdf2cffb\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/recommend/20170530/1129229</a><br />\n<br />\n嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9083e1af2fe1111b2c69addc82aae1bb3ca1ed42","tid":263857,"uid":118990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T11:02:15.000Z","msg":"個老師確係堅喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b75882cd8e91649834bdabd4f96fa4623c1e500","tid":263857,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個老師確係堅喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輸了比賽要啪啪"},{"pid":"08e19d2b8061eb13ff706bd9464e72e57273ede2","tid":263857,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"日本教育界老師痴咗線情有可原"},{"pid":"b269fd30496954b0c93a25743702ba14ee1d2092","tid":263857,"uid":118990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r